        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes, very much so. I didn't think you'd manage to come right away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x54,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Uu, you didn't trust in me...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But seeing how you made it, I guess you're fine. You can come every week too, you know?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Though it would have been more impressive if you had come from the start."
